{"id":18071,"date":"2022-12-31T04:29:44","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:29:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-o-to.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:29:44","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:29:44","slug":"ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-o-to","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-o-to\/","title":{"rendered":"\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng linh ki\u1ec7n b\u00e1n d\u1eabn Infineon trong s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>C\u00e1c linh ki\u1ec7n b\u00e1n d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Infineon bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn, vi \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n\u2026 gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea3m ph\u00e1t th\u1ea3i kh\u00ed nh\u00e0 k\u00ednh.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Infineon Technologies AG l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n d\u1eabn \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i CO2.  Danh m\u1ee5c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Infineon bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chip ri\u00eang l\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Chipset \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Infineon bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn, b\u1ed9 vi \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n, tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u00e1n d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m chi ph\u00ed v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.  Danh m\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5t b\u00e1n d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Infineon bao g\u1ed3m xe \u0111i\u1ec7n, xe \u0111i\u1ec7n hybrid v\u00e0 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n hybrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i (xEV), c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 b\u1ed9 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n cho \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd pin v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ea1c.  tr\u00ean xe (OBC).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ea1c xe h\u01a1i<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ea1c pin \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p cao trong xe plug-in hybrid (PHEV) ho\u1eb7c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n (EV) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec7n trong khi xe \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed7 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1m\/tr\u1ea1m s\u1ea1c gi\u00fap t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ea1c.  Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn \u1eafc quy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 2 chi\u1ec1u (n\u1ed1i \u1eafc quy v\u1edbi t\u1ea3i ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c \u1eafc quy t\u1eeb tram v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i CO2 tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Infineon\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png\" title=\"ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-600x369.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">B\u1ed9 s\u1ea1c OBC gi\u00fap t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ea1c pin.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd pin (BMS)<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Do b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, cell pin r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u00f2ng x\u1ea3\/n\u1ea1p, \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00ean pin c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a BMS.  BMS gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng \u00f4 pin.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">BMS v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111o nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9, \u00e1p su\u1ea5t, d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p, \u0111o dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea1c v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c.  D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i s\u1ea1c (SoC), t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a pin (SoH) v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nhu c\u1ea7u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i CO2 tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Infineon - 1\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_300_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png\" title=\"1672425604_300_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_300_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-300x219.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_300_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png 480w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">BMS g\u1eafn c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a BMS l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 pin kh\u1ecfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c ng\u1eaft k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i pin.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh (hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o), \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u (DC) th\u00e0nh d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n xoay chi\u1ec1u (AC) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.  Bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 quay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ngu\u1ed3n \u0111i\u1ec7n xoay chi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i CO2 tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Infineon - 2\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_275_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png\" title=\"1672425604_275_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_275_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat-300x219.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425604_275_ung-dung-linh-kien-ban-dan-infineon-trong-san-xuat.png 480w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Infineon ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Infineon c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n d\u1eabn r\u1eddi gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a chi ph\u00ed t\u1eeb v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n chung c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh \u00f4 t\u00f4 v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t.  .  Nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong khi gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p Infineon t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Lan Anh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1c linh ki\u1ec7n b\u00e1n d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Infineon bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn, vi \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n\u2026 gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea3m ph\u00e1t th\u1ea3i kh\u00ed nh\u00e0 k\u00ednh. Infineon Technologies AG l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n d\u1eabn \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17277,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18071"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18071"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18071\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/17277"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18071"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18071"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18071"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}